high_descs: Turn to the microwave above the stove
Open the microwave door and take out the mug
Turn right and walk around the counter to the refrigerator
Put the mug on the top shelf to the left of the tomato, close the door then open it and take out the mug
Turn left and walk around the counter to the shelves on the right
Put the mug on the middle shelf in front of the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Cool a mug and put it on a wooden shelf

high_descs: take out a mug from the microwave
turn around and head to the fridge
place the mug to cool in the fridge and take it out
turn around and head to the shelf
place the mug on the shelf
anns.task_desc: place a cold mug on the shelf

high_descs: Turn around to face the microwave above the stove.
Take the mug out of the microwave.
Turn right, bring the mug to the sink, turn right, go down to the fridge and face the fridge on the left.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Bring the mug left to the sink, turn left, go past the counter to the wooden rack in the corner.
Put the mug on the second shelf of the wooden rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the wooden rack.
